# ─── Amplify / AppSync credential overrides ───────────────────────────────────
#
# These variables are OPTIONAL.  The app reads its AppSync endpoint and API key
# from amplify/amplify_outputs.json (regenerated by `npx ampx pipeline-deploy`
# during every CI/CD build).  Set these only when you need to override that
# file — for example if the committed copy has a stale API key.
#
# In the AWS Amplify Console:  App settings → Environment variables
# For local development:       copy to .env.local (gitignored via *.local)
#
# VITE_APPSYNC_URL=https://<api-id>.appsync-api.<region>.amazonaws.com/graphql
# VITE_APPSYNC_API_KEY=da2-<your-api-key>

# ─── RDS / Lambda secrets (set in Amplify Console → Secrets, NOT here) ────────
#
# DB_HOST   MySQL host
# DB_USER   MySQL username
# DB_PASS   MySQL password
# DB_NAME   MySQL database name
# DB_PORT   MySQL port (default 3306)
